GUI CHOICE CSV2_IN_SKIP_DUPLICATE_DELIMITERS_CSV2_2 Yes%No Skip Duplicate Delimiters:
DEFAULT_MACRO CSV2_IN_FIELD_QUALIFIER_CHARACTER_CSV2_2 <quote>
